Financia is a "free" software product for the financial accounting and managerial accounting. 

Features :
=======

1. Multi level account head hierarchy

2. Multi costcenter support

3. User defined voucher types

4. Multi currency support

5. Multi language support

6. Double Entry Book keeping

7. Financial accounting reports such as ledgers, day book, trial balance, profit & loss account and balance sheet with drill-down facilities

8. Various graphical time-line reports 
9. Integrated Budgetting support

10. Integrated tax management System

11. Magento Integration Support

12. Role based user level security

13. Sophisticated data backup and recovery of the sytem


Technologies
==========

1. PHP 5

2. MySQL

3. Zend Framework 1.11.4

4. JQuery


